@UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5034

### ── Applications ──────────────────────────────────────

### List all applications (to find AppId values)
GET {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/applications
Accept: application/json

### ── Users ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List users (paginated, optional search)
GET {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### ── Access Requests ───────────────────────────────────

### 1. Submit a new access request
POST {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/access-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "mahores",
  "email": "shubham.mahore@dnow.com",
  "appRoleId": 3
}

### 2. List access requests (filter by status)
GET {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/access-requests?status=Pending
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get a specific access request by ID
GET {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/access-requests/47
Accept: application/json

### 4. Approve an access request
PATCH {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/access-requests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Approved"
}

### 5. Fulfill an access request (grants the role in UserRoles)
PATCH {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/access-requests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Fulfilled"
}

### ── Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Look up user roles by username
POST {{UserAccessManager.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/user-roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "mahores",
  "allowedRoles": "MATSEARCH,LDE"
}

###
